      "date": "2013-04-25 18:02:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nIt is likely that http://review.whamcloud.com/6102 will land before this patch, so this patch should also fix up the comment that Mike made in mdt_intent_layout():\n\n        mdt_object_put(info->mti_env, obj);\n\t\t\t\t\n I think the natural place for that is mdt_lvbo_size() and I\n assume you use mdt_intent_layout() just because lu_env is\n available here. Please add comment that it is better to move\n this into mdt_lvbo_size() after http://review.whamcloud.com/5497\n which adds lu_env to ldlm functions",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 6
    },
